        "description": "<p>Christmas decorations plugin for WordPress. Decorate your WordPress website with Christmas trees, Santa, snowfall or just display a pop-up to remember your visitors that it&#8217;s Christmas.</p>\n<p><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"750\" height=\"422\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/AXo0mqt1ZNg?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></p>\n<p>Features:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Christmas Pop-ups</li>\n<li>Snowfall animations</li>\n<li>Christmas decorations</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Admin Features:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Manage decorations</li>\n<li>Enable/Disable snowfall</li>\n<li>Manage popups</li>\n</ul>\n<p>For further information and instructions please see the <a href=\"https://pixolette.com/wordpress-plugins/christmas-panda/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">plugin page</a></p>\n",
        "installation": "<p>The quickest method for installing the Christmas Panda is:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Visit Plugins -&gt; Upload Plugin -&gt; Choose File &#8220;christmas-panda.zip&#8221;</li>\n<li>Click &#8220;Install Now&#8221;</li>\n<li>Finally click &#8220;Activate Plugin&#8221;</li>\n</ol>\n<p>If you would prefer to do things manually then follow these instructions:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Upload the <code>halloween-panda</code> folder to the <code>/wp-content/plugins/</code> directory</li>\n<li>Activate the plugin through the &#8216;Plugins&#8217; menu in WordPress</li>\n</ol>\n",
        "changelog": "<h4>1.0.4</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Minor fixes, tested with WordPress 5.5.3</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.0.3</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Minor fixes, tested with WordPress 4.9</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.0.2</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Added banner in dashboard</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.0.1</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed bug -&gt; when snowfall is active to not add padding on top/bottom of the page</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.0.0</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Initial release</li>\n</ul>\n"
    },
